name: Jump From A Building Free
description:
This is the free version of Jump From A Building

The stickman wants to be a superhero. The first thing he’s going to do is to jump from a building and survive… a hard task for him. Luckily, he gets something useful, umbrellas. How to use them is up to you. Can the stickman become a real superhero? His fate is in your hand!

Don’t think this game is an easy one. To survive with limited number umbrella, you’ll need nerves of steel and smart strategy.

Now come and enjoy the stickman’s adventure.

Full version Link: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/jump-from-a-building/id464654559?ls=1&mt=8
